# 🎯 Claude Recruiter Skills

> **IT** — Framework di skill per Claude pensato per recruiter IT: freelance, consulenti in agenzia e Talent Acquisition interni.  
> **EN** — A Claude skill framework built for IT recruiters: freelancers, agency consultants, and in-house Talent Acquisition.

