Fonte / Source: Schema Retributivo Candidati ufficiale — valori indicativi / official, indicative values.  
Costo azienda / Employer cost ≈ RAL × 1.30

| RAL | Netto/mese 13 men. | Netto/mese 14 men. |
|---|---|---|
| €30.000 | €1.757 | €1.645 |
| €40.000 | €2.122 | €1.972 |
